          Real Caffeine Calculator is provided for general informational and educational purposes only. The caffeine estimates produced by this tool are based on published average values and a standard pharmacokinetic half-life model. Actual caffeine metabolism varies significantly between individuals based on genetics, age, body weight, liver function, medications, and other factors.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px;">
          Nothing on this Site constitutes medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult a qualified healthcare professional before making decisions about caffeine consumption, especially if you have a medical condition, are pregnant, or are taking medications that may interact with caffeine.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #ededed; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;">
          Accuracy of information
        </h2>
        <p>
          We make reasonable efforts to keep caffeine values and scientific information accurate and up to date. However, we make no representations or warranties — express or implied — about the completeness, accuracy, reliability, or suitability of the information on the Site. Caffeine content in commercial beverages may vary by batch, location, preparation method, and over time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #ededed; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;">
          Limitation of liability
        </h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Real Caffeine Calculator and its operators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of or reliance on this Site or the information it provides. This includes but is not limited to health decisions made based on the calculator's output.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #ededed; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;">
          Intellectual property
        </h2>
        <p>
          All content on the Site, including text, design, code, and graphics, is owned by or licensed to Real Caffeine Calculator. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without prior written permission.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #ededed; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;">
          Third-party links
        </h2>
        <p>
          The Site may contain links to third-party websites. These links are provided for convenience only. We have no control over, and assume no responsibility for, the content or practices of any third-party sites.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #ededed; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.3px;">
          Changes to terms
        </h2>
